headline: Rockwell Automation Set to Report Q1 Earnings: What's in Store?
summary: ROK to report 1Q26 results on Feb. 5, with EPS expected to rise 38.8% y/y to $2.54.

headline: Rockwell Automation (ROK) Q1 Earnings on the Horizon: Analysts' Insights on Key Performance Measures
summary: Besides Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimates for Rockwell Automation (ROK), review projections for some of its key metrics to gain a deeper understanding of how the company might have fared during the quarter ended December 2025.
